pattern_preservation.interpretation: Moderate pattern preservation - some structural similarity remains
pattern_preservation.description: How well rank ordering of community connections is preserved relative to universe

generation_fidelity.interpretation: Good generation fidelity - graphs reasonably match targets
generation_fidelity.description: How well graphs match their scaled probability targets (P_sub)

degree_consistency.interpretation: Weak degree-community relationship - limited correlation with centers
degree_consistency.description: How well actual node degrees correlate with universe degree centers

overall.interpretation: Low overall consistency - family shows significant structural variation
overall.description: Weighted average of all consistency metrics
